<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
        <title>${title}</title>
    </head>

    <body>
        <div style="font-size:16px; padding-top: 20px">
            Hello,
            <br/><br/>
            This is an automated alert to inform you that the request has reached the maximum number of fail retries. Please find below the request detail:
            <br/><br/>
            <strong>Request Detail:</strong>
            <br/>
            Http Status Code : ${statusCode}
	        <br/>
	        End Point URL : ${endPointURL}
